  "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1) Right click on a user and select \"Send Contract Request\" from the menu\r\n2) Enter a message that includes the \"'\" character. For example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nHi, it's Zahary from the Nimbus team\r\n```\r\n\r\n3) Once the contact request is accepted, you'll notice that your chat history with the new contact starts with your contact request message, but it has been translated to the following:\r\n\r\n```\r\nHi, it&#039;s Zahary from the Nimbus team\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nI expect to see the original contract request message that I entered.\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: Status 0.8\r\n- Operating System: macOS\r\n\r\n",
