    "body": "Utils.qml:\r\n```qml\r\n    function escapeHtml(unsafeStr)\r\n    {\r\n        return unsafeStr\r\n            .replace(/&/g, \"&amp;\")\r\n            .replace(/</g, \"&lt;\")\r\n            .replace(/>/g, \"&gt;\")\r\n            .replace(/\"/g, \"&quot;\")\r\n            .replace(/'/g, \"&#039;\");\r\n    }\r\n```",
